OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1781394469
OL,3,CChannel Islands to follow UK in
OL,4,Coffering meningitis B vaccine to young
OL,5,Cpeople
OL,7,FJersey will follow the UK in offering
OL,8,Fa meningitis B vaccine to year 13
OL,9,Fpupils and new university starters,
OL,10,Fwhilst officials in Guernsey say they
OL,11,Fare "working on a local offer".
OL,13,FThe UK government announced today (12
OL,14,FJune) that more than one million young
OL,15,Fpeople would be offered the two-dose
OL,16,Fvaccine through pharmacies.
OL,18,FIt comes after an outbreak in Kent
OL,19,Fearlier this year, as well as clusters
OL,20,Fof infections in Dorset and Reading.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/4
