CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1781394469
OL,3,CChannel Islands to follow UK in
OL,4,Coffering meningitis B vaccine to young
OL,5,Cpeople
OL,7,FMeningitis can be an extremely
OL,8,Fdangerous condition and affects people
OL,9,Fof all ages. It is most common in
OL,10,Fbabies, young children, and young
OL,11,Fadults.
OL,13,FAlthough babies have been offered a
OL,14,Fvaccine since 2015, those over the age
OL,15,Fof 11 have not received the jab.
OL,17,FThose set to start university are
OL,18,Fdeemed more at risk because they are
OL,19,Flikely to be living in shared
OL,20,Faccommodation.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/4
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
