OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,354,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1781394469
OL,3,CChannel Islands to follow UK in
OL,4,Coffering meningitis B vaccine to young
OL,5,Cpeople
OL,7,FEmma Baker, Health Protection Senior
OL,8,FNurse Advisor at Public Health in
OL,9,FJersey, said that the offer "will be
OL,10,Fextended to Jersey students" and they
OL,11,Fhad been "working closely with UK
OL,12,Fpartners". Full details of the rollout
OL,13,Fare expected in the coming days.
OL,15,FIn Guernsey, Alex Hawkins-Drew,
OL,16,FAssociate Director at Public Health,
OL,17,Fsaid that they were "aware of the
OL,18,Fprogramme planned in the UK and
OL,19,Fworking on a local offer", but plans
OL,20,Ffor the Bailiwick are not expected to
OL,21,Fbe released for a couple of weeks.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/4
